Key generation

create user with username and password

ssh-keygen -command to generate key

key will be generated in .ssh folder under home/user or under root


nodes(slaves) should have public key

etc/ssh/ssh_config - to set key -permitRootlogin:yes

then open authorized_keys(inside .ssh) and copy public key

ping ipaddress - to ping the server

ssh root@ipAddress - to login to slave from master - look for id_rsa private key(else use -i and mention path of id_rsa)

etc/hosts - to rename ip with specific name

